note: I own both residential and commercial real estate in North Iowa. I spent about 25 years in the Violence Against Women field, both providing counseling and advocacy services and teaching self-defense classes. I have been married for almost 30 years and have 23-year-old twin boys. I'm on the Board of Directors for the Mason City Chamber of Commerce, the North Iowa Landlord Association, and the League of Women Voters of North Iowa. I also founded the Business Ladies of Iowa Networking Group.
